      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIRETHORN (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with seven wins and two minors from 12 tries. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (41.30) in a OPEN last time at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. GOLDSTAR PRADA (8) was a OPEN winner two back then out of the placings latest at this track but moves to Box 8 this time where she has performed well. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. MOET MAGIC (2) thrives over the longer races. Was too tough when scoring last time over 710m at this track in a Grade 5/6 (41.71). Is yet to taste defeat in two tries at this distance. Leading chance again. LAKEVIEW HUNTER (1) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
